---
// HowToStart Section - Getting started guide with download
import Button from './Button.astro';
---

<section class="section how-to-start" id="how-to-start">
	<div class="container-narrow">
		<h2>How to Get Started</h2>
		<p class="section-intro">
			Adopting spec-driven development is straightforward. Follow these steps to transform your workflow:
		</p>

		<div class="steps-timeline">
			<div class="step">
				<div class="step-marker">
					<span class="step-number">1</span>
					<div class="connector"></div>
				</div>
				<div class="step-content">
					<h3>Download the Spec Architect Agent</h3>
					<p>Get our free Claude Code agent that guides you through creating perfect specifications. It handles Requirements â†’ Design â†’ Tasks automatically.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="step">
				<div class="step-marker">
					<span class="step-number">2</span>
					<div class="connector"></div>
				</div>
				<div class="step-content">
					<h3>Install in Your Project</h3>
					<p>Place <code>spec-architect.md</code> in your <code>.claude/agents/</code> directory. The agent becomes available in all Claude Code sessions for that project.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="step">
				<div class="step-marker">
					<span class="step-number">3</span>
					<div class="connector"></div>
				</div>
				<div class="step-content">
					<h3>Start with a Feature</h3>
					<p>Pick any upcoming feature. Ask Claude to use spec mode. The agent will walk you through Requirements, Design, and Tasks phases with approval gates.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="step">
				<div class="step-marker">
					<span class="step-number">4</span>
					<div class="connector"></div>
				</div>
				<div class="step-content">
					<h3>Review and Approve</h3>
					<p>At each gate, review the spec. Request changes, ask questions, or approve to continue. The spec becomes your single source of truth.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="step">
				<div class="step-marker">
					<span class="step-number">5</span>
					<div class="connector-last"></div>
				</div>
				<div class="step-content">
					<h3>Let AI Build It</h3>
					<p>Hand the completed spec to Claude for implementation. Watch as it builds exactly what you planned, tracking progress against your criteria.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="pro-tip">
			<h4>ðŸ’¡ Pro Tip</h4>
			<p>Start with a small, well-defined feature for your first spec. As you get comfortable with the process, tackle larger projects. The agent scales from quick fixes to multi-week initiatives.</p>
		</div>

		<!-- Download CTA -->
		<div class="download-cta" id="download">
			<h3>Ready to Get Started?</h3>
			<p class="download-intro">
				Download the free Spec Architect agent and transform your workflow today.
			</p>

			<Button href="/downloads/spec-architect.md" variant="primary" size="lg">
				<svg width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
					<path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"></path>
					<polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"></polyline>
					<line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3"></line>
				</svg>
				Download spec-architect.md
			</Button>
			<p class="file-info">Free â€¢ 29KB â€¢ No signup required</p>

			<div class="support-note">
				<svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
					<path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"></path>
				</svg>
				<div>
					<strong>Love this tool?</strong> Payment options coming soon. For now, it's completely free with no restrictions.
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.how-to-start {
		background: var(--color-white);
	}

	.section-intro {
		font-size: var(--text-xl);
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
		color: var(--color-text-secondary);
	}

	.steps-timeline {
		margin: var(--space-12) 0;
	}

	.step {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 60px 1fr;
		gap: var(--space-6);
		margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
	}

	.step-marker {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
	}

	.step-number {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		width: 60px;
		height: 60px;
		background: var(--color-accent);
		color: var(--color-gray-900);
		border-radius: 50%;
		font-size: var(--text-2xl);
		font-weight: 900;
		flex-shrink: 0;
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-brutal-sm);
		border: var(--border-width) solid var(--color-border);
	}

	.connector {
		width: 4px;
		flex-grow: 1;
		background: var(--color-gray-900);
		margin: var(--space-2) 0;
	}

	.connector-last {
		width: 4px;
		height: 40px;
		background: var(--color-gray-900);
		margin: var(--space-2) 0;
	}

	.step-content {
		padding: var(--space-4) 0;
	}

	.step-content h3 {
		font-size: var(--text-2xl);
		margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
		color: var(--color-text-primary);
	}

	.step-content p {
		font-size: var(--text-lg);
		line-height: 1.7;
		margin-bottom: 0;
		color: var(--color-text-secondary);
	}

	.pro-tip {
		background: var(--color-pastel-yellow);
		padding: var(--space-8);
		border-radius: var(--border-radius);
		border: var(--border-width) solid var(--color-border);
		margin-top: var(--space-16);
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-brutal);
	}

	.pro-tip h4 {
		font-size: var(--text-2xl);
		margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
		color: var(--color-gray-900);
	}

	.pro-tip p {
		font-size: var(--text-lg);
		margin-bottom: 0;
		line-height: 1.7;
	}

	/* Download CTA */
	.download-cta {
		margin-top: var(--space-16);
		text-align: center;
		padding: var(--space-12);
		background: var(--color-white);
		border: var(--border-width) solid var(--color-border);
		border-radius: var(--border-radius);
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-brutal-lg);
	}

	.download-cta h3 {
		font-size: var(--text-3xl);
		margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
		color: var(--color-gray-900);
	}

	.download-intro {
		font-size: var(--text-xl);
		color: var(--color-text-secondary);
		margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
	}

	.file-info {
		font-size: var(--text-sm);
		color: var(--color-text-secondary);
		margin-top: var(--space-3);
	}

	.support-note {
		margin-top: var(--space-8);
		padding: var(--space-4);
		background: var(--color-pastel-yellow);
		border-radius: var(--border-radius);
		border: var(--border-width) solid var(--color-border);
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: var(--space-3);
		font-size: var(--text-sm);
		color: var(--color-gray-700);
	}

	.support-note svg {
		color: var(--color-danger);
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}

	.support-note strong {
		color: var(--color-gray-900);
	}

	@media (max-width: 640px) {
		.step {
			grid-template-columns: 50px 1fr;
			gap: var(--space-4);
		}

		.step-number {
			width: 50px;
			height: 50px;
			font-size: var(--text-xl);
		}
	}
</style>
